what about it?

56
00:03:35,959 --> 00:03:39,289
And so, our crazy
field day ended.

57
00:03:39,459 --> 00:03:41,319
We had just started
a new month,

58
00:03:41,429 --> 00:03:44,359
and already the school festival
was waiting for us.

59
00:03:44,499 --> 00:03:48,559
Right now, our prefectural high school
is preparing for it.

60
00:03:50,069 --> 00:03:52,589
By the way, the class that
