Why?

70
00:04:22,939 --> 00:04:25,629
The reason was because the girl
striding boldly beside me

71
00:04:25,799 --> 00:04:28,299
said the following,
and for no other reason.

72
00:04:29,239 --> 00:04:31,899
Announcing the results of a survey?
How dumb can you get?

73
00:04:32,039 --> 00:04:37,179
What's fun about that?
I don't get it at all!

74
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:40,479
Then you should have
spoken up earlier.

75
00:04:40,889 --> 00:04:42,449
You saw the troubled look
on Mr. Okabe's face,

76
