And yet it would seem that
you had something to do

82
00:04:55,669 --> 00:04:57,999
with our class winning
the field day.

83
00:04:58,139 --> 00:05:03,729
You took part in most of the track-related
competitions and won all of them, right?

84
00:05:04,239 --> 00:05:05,939
Or was that someone else?

85
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:08,309
This and that are
two different things.

86
00:05:08,479 --> 00:05:10,139
This is the school festival
we're talking about!

87
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:13,579
It's the one vitally important
super event that we get in a year.

88
00:05:13,789 --> 00:05:16,119
- Is that so?
- It is!

89
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:20,049
We're going to do something
really exciting!

90
00:05:20,189 --> 00:05:22,389
As she said that, Haruhi's face
looked like Hannibal's

91
00:05:22,529 --> 00:05:26,729
as he crossed the Alps during
the Second Punic War.

92
00:05:26,869 --> 00:05:29,539
Confident and shining bright.

93
